README:

1.) Install the "mediawiki" plugin in your Etherpad Lite through "/admin/plugins"
2.) Add ep_mediawiki to your settings.json:
    "ep_MediaWiki_default": true
3.) Copy all wikipad.* files to a location that can not be accessed remotely.
4.) Install https://hg.nhg.name/unchroot/
5.) Configure wikipad.conf.phs and make sure that all paths are accessible.
6.) Configure CRON to call wikipad.phs regularly:
    */5 * * * * root php /path/to/wikipad.phs >/dev/null 2>&1
